NHANES Exploratory Data Analysis

Updated on : Fri Nov 18 23:03:45 2022

configuration DB

sqlHost <- "localhost"
sqlUserName <- "sa"
sqlPassword <- "yourStrong(!)Password"
sqlDefaultDb <- "NhanesLandingZone"

Load libs

library(naniar)
library(visdat)
library(phonto)

Missing value in Row

demo = phonto::nhanes('DEMO_E')

Plot missing pattern

vis_miss(demo,warn_large_data=FALSE)

Missing pattern across age

gg_miss_fct(demo,fct = RIDAGEYR)

show missing percentage

gg_miss_var(demo,show_pct = TRUE)
